{"tid":899926,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone「遇氦」集體死機？真相原來係咁...","createTime":"2018-11-12T23:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T15:21:20.000Z","uid":54870,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f29735844be5ef1432079d83dcbbef4266412057","tid":899926,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T23:57:11.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，美國芝加哥附近的莫里斯醫院(Morris Hospital)安裝磁力共振的設備時，赫然發現醫院內所有的Apple裝置，包括iPhone及Apple Watch均突然死機，事件更引發外國網友熱議。最終，該醫院的系統專家Erik Wooldrige證實原來一切是由於「氦氣」作怪。<br />\n<br />\n在這次離奇事故背後，隱藏着數個巧合。Wooldrige表示，磁力共振機的超導磁體須長期浸在液態氦中，以維持正常運作。但這次安裝過程中出現了氦氣洩露；而剛好由於該醫院磁力共振房的冷氣系統與全院相通，導致氦氣在醫院內不斷循環，接觸到所有人的Apple產品。<br />\n<br />\n更加巧合的是，自iPhone 6以後，Apple採用了「矽基微機電系統」的SiT512計時電子振盪器，而非傳統的石英震盪器；而氦氣能夠穿過矽晶接合的氧化物，影響儀器運作。結果，所有人都發現自己的Apple產品都出現不同程度的失靈；而其他Andriod手機卻安然無恙。"},{"pid":"7e61458ddc375a6e9273f914a9af53eedd121b1a","tid":899926,"uid":36893,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:01:41.000Z","msg":"係咪想俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"ea5142f2924ea9c02b0c5d09f0da0d463c5f7d08","tid":899926,"uid":53466,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:01:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbdb9d1b58909858518daab03ff93e327f398ca6","tid":899926,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:04:19.000Z","msg":"樓主你有十秒鐘"},{"pid":"bb3886509638103a36260e206873fda4b39ad675","tid":899926,"uid":54870,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"7e61458ddc375a6e9273f914a9af53eedd121b1a","tid":899926,"uid":36893,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:01:41.000Z","msg":"係咪想俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eEEFSxG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"